$DEF_BOITE
Gosub HORODAT From WGOPOO
If dim(A_WINDPREV)<=0 : Local Char A_WINDPREV(30) : Endif
Local Inpbox "OPOO" From GFONCTION At A_STAMP With A_WINDPREV Mask [POO0]
&  Listbox [POO_] GAU_CHE
&   [L]SAIRAP(1) = [F:POO]POO Using "K:10c" Titled TITSEL(1) ,
&   [L]SAIRAP(2) = [F:POO]DES Using "K:30X" Titled TITSEL(2) ,
&   [L]SAIRAP(3) = [F:POO]DESSHO Using "K:10X" Titled TITSEL(3)
&  Listbox [POO9] GAU_CHE9
&   [L]SAIRAP(1) = [F:POO9]A_TAB1 Using "K:10c" Titled TITSEL9(1)  ,
&   [L]SAIRAP(2) = [F:POO9]A_TAB2 Using "K:30X" Titled TITSEL9(2)  ,
&   [L]SAIRAP(3) = [F:POO9]A_TAB3 Using "K:10X" Titled TITSEL9(3) 
&  Listbox [BAN_] GAU_CHE1
&   [L]SAIRAP(1) = [F:BAN]BAN Using "K:5c" Titled TITSEL1(1) ,
&   [L]SAIRAP(2) = [F:BAN]DES Using "K:30X" Titled TITSEL1(2) ,
&   [L]SAIRAP(3) = [F:BAN]CPY Using "K:5c" Titled TITSEL1(3) ,
&   [L]SAIRAP(4) = [F:BAN]CUR Using "K:3c" Titled TITSEL1(4)
& As [POO0]
Titled [POO0] TIT
Return

